title: Super Cyborg Steam Edition v1 23-TE
description:
Super Cyborg is an oldschool nonstop hardcore run 'n' gun action! You play as battle cyborg who was sent to investigate the mysterious island. A very powerful alien life form known as ' Xirxul ' has been awakened by the scientists and now all humanity is in danger! Rush through 7 levels filled with countless monsters and creatures. Destroy everything that moves! 8-bit stylized pixelart graphics combined with awesome chiptune soundtrack creates the perfect atmosphere for brutal bio-science fiction setting.
Only the fittest will survive in this world is sickening.

System requirements
-Windows XP, Vista, Windows 7, Windows 8
-Pentium 4 800 MHz or equivalent
-512 MB RAM
-ATI or NVidia card w/256 MB RAM
-100 MB of available space

-Install
-Play
